{synoptline}
{synopt:{it:{help int:nodes}}}number of nodes{p_end}
{synopt:{opth k(int)}}number of neighhbors on ring-lattice on each side{p_end}
{synopt:{opth prob(float)}}probability for a tie to rewire{p_end}
